cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.IR 

This paper deals with a machine learning algorithm, specifically an ensemble model of boosted regression trees, and proposes a novel approach to address a common issue in the algorithm. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as these sub-categories are closely related to machine learning. The paper also evaluates the proposed approach on large scale datasets, indicating a focus on practical applications, which suggests the sub-categories cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as possible additional categories.
